# Training programs photo folders live here.
#
# Convention: each program in data/training-programs.json has a `slug`.
# Create a folder with that exact name and drop photos as 01.jpg, 02.jpg, …
#
# Example for slug "2026-04-knee-cadaver-chennai":
#   images/training/2026-04-knee-cadaver-chennai/01.jpg
#   images/training/2026-04-knee-cadaver-chennai/02.jpg
#   …
#
# Then in the admin (_tools/catalog-editor.html → Training tab → Edit),
# set Photo count = NN. The page automatically renders 01-NN.jpg with
# onerror=hide so any missing numbers vanish silently.
